In Need for Speed: The Run, you race across America.
The review
A carefree drive turns into a routine morning shift ride because of a series of completely unnecessary careless mistakes.
While the ambition has been largely fulfilled, it is worthless if no one has shown any willingness to do anything extra.
The new volume, subtitled The Run, was highly anticipated before its release.
