"In an aggressive tone, she said, 'You shouldn't put your daughter by the door,'" Roseanna Monk said.
I said, "I don't care what you think".
She became angry and began to speak obscenely - shouting out the simplest of expressions...
She had a bottle of water on her and started spitting water at me.
He says Genevieve had a hysterical fit.
"I said to the woman, 'Look what you did to my daughter.'"
LaBelle threw herself at her mother, who was still holding Genevieve, and was stopped by her escort, who then dragged her to a waiting car, Roseanna Monk said.
Meanwhile, the daughter screamed so loudly she threw up, adding.
